{"data":[{"date":"03:08 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham 3-1 Fulham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-tottenham-31-fulham.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb kh\u00e1c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">9 &ndash; Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 9 trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Fulham t\u1ea1i Premier League, ch\u1ec9 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n19 &ndash; Fulham \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 19 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh (t\u00ednh trong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 n\u0103m nay).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n19 &ndash; Spurs \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 19 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham 3-1 Fulham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham 3-1 Fulham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-Tottenham-3-1-Fulham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kane h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8, gi\u00fap Tottenham h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Fulham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n1065 - B\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Fulham l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Kane ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8 sau 1065 ph\u00fat t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 &ndash; Sessegnon \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Fulham tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (1 b\u00e0n, 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n13 &ndash; K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Fulham v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2, Mitrovic \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Mohamed Salah (14) l\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n trong s\u1ed1 4 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6 &ndash; Moura \u0111\u00e3 in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 7 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham (2 b\u00e0n, 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n24 &ndash; Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi 24 b\u00e0n sau 36 tr\u1eadn derby London cho Tottenham (trung b\u00ecnh 0.67 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn). Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal l\u00e0 Thierry Henry c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 10 tr\u1eadn derby London tr\u1edf l\u00ean (43 b\u00e0n trong 59 tr\u1eadn &ndash; trung b\u00ecnh 0.73 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham vs Fulham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-tottenham-vs-fulham-31-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194766.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tottenham 3-1 Fulham (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-hoa-giai-loi-nguyen-thang-8-172-194769.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2517","checkdouble":"194770"},{"date":"03:19 19/08","title":"Hazard: \"Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u1eeba v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 gay c\u1ea5n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Chelsea v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pedro v\u00e0 Morata. Nh\u01b0ng Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c HLV Sarri sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHazard ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 60 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n do ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 Alonso ki\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng Hazard t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. V\u1eady n\u00ean d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 hay 20 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1eabu HLV mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i th\u00ec r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n m\u1ecdi l\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ma thu\u1eadt. V\u1eady n\u00ean th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede Premier League, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. Sarri th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2516","checkdouble":"194771"},{"date":"03:32 19/08","title":"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n Premier League, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a The Gunners \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho Chelsea \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Emery \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi v\u00f2ng 2 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London n\u1eefa. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2515","checkdouble":"194772"},{"date":"03:43 19/08","title":"Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan sau tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Emery. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e1t dao ch\u00ed t\u1eed c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan khi th\u1ea5y m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua Man City ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu 3 b\u00e0n thua. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 3-2 nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c \u0111i n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Chelsea th\u1eadt ra c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n. C\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p s\u00e1t hay ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n trao cho h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00f2n Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 3-2. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111i nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf. Trong hi\u1ec7p hai, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 19 v\u00e0 21 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang d\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-chelsea-vs-arsenal-32-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194768.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2514","checkdouble":"194773"},{"date":"03:56 19/08","title":"Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/pochettino-noi-khung-sau-khi-bi-hoi-ve-tuong-lai-alderweireld.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i gi\u1eadn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi b\u1ecb c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Alderweireld.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Fulham sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Alderweireld v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Spurs.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Alderweireld ra \u0111i v\u1eabn tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/pochettino-noi-khung-sau-khi-bi-hoi-ve-tuong-lai-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham, HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Alderweireld. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3i li\u00ean h\u1ed3i trong v\u00f2ng 5 ph\u00fat. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f3m t\u1eaft l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Pochettino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n, v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. Khi \u0111\u00f3, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Levy v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ed1c to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Kh\u00f4ng ai n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-tottenham-vs-fulham-31-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194766.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tottenham 3-1 Fulham (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-hoa-giai-loi-nguyen-thang-8-172-194769.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2513","checkdouble":"194774"},{"date":"04:06 19/08","title":"Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n Premier League, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a The Gunners \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho Chelsea \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Emery \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi v\u00f2ng 2 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London n\u1eefa. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2512","checkdouble":"194775"},{"date":"04:20 19/08","title":"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League trong v\u00f2ng 26 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. Sau 22 n\u0103m n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Wenger, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Arsenal c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh sang m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 HLV Emery. Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City. Ti\u1ebfp ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecba Stamford Bridge c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Arsenal trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n khi Arsenal l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. <strong>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 1992/93</strong>. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Arsenal m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn thua 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Norwich tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Blackburn \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGeorge Graham l\u00e0 HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1992/93 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Steve Burtenshaw.</strong> Khi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n, Burtenshaw \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00e1ng 3 \u2013 th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 1986.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2511","checkdouble":"194776"},{"date":"04:30 19/08","title":"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thu v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u00fap Chelsea th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 v\u1edbi The Blues. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn e d\u00e8 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn e d\u00e8 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKh\u00f4ng, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong 25 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p s\u00e1t t\u1ea7m cao kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i c\u0169ng x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o thay Willian \u1edf ph\u00fat 60. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Alonso ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u00ean cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 25-30 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n cao. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong v\u00f2ng 1 tu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 90 ph\u00fat\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2510","checkdouble":"194777"},{"date":"05:26 19/08","title":"3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/3-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thang-tung-bung-cua-chelsea-truoc-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong khi Chelsea th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb v\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c th\u1eb3m. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a hai b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung l\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Chelsea l\u1eabn Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 khi Arsenal li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Bellerin v\u00e0 Monreal. N\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal ch\u01b0a v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u00f4ng lui v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu 2 b\u00e0n thua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat 81. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Marcos Alonso b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Arsenal v\u00e0 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho Pedro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, Bellerin b\u1ecb h\u00fat theo Willian v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng lui v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Alonso g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Alonso di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Arsenal m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n d\u00e2ng qu\u00e1 cao. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda sau h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t trong top 4 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00e1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Granit Xhaka n\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Xhaka c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, Xhaka v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng Xhaka kh\u00f4ng s\u1eeda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xhaka\" title=\"Xhaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xhaka ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, Xhaka li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft khi tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Xhaka c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 Arsenal ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e2ng cao. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu trao cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng th\u00ec b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi Xhaka c\u00f2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Arsenal kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee7 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 cao h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, Arsenal thi tri\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 Xhaka ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Torreira v\u00e0 Guendouzi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. N\u1ebfu HLV Emery mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, &ldquo;tr\u1ea3m&rdquo; Xhaka l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n khi c\u00f3 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sang ph\u00fat 60, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao Eden Hazard v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i mang t\u00ednh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 30 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng Hazard \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Arsenal nhi\u1ec1u phen cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Alonso l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/052423-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o cho Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Hazard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 l\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng Hazard s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Newcastle v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Willian \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng anh thi\u1ebfu \u0111i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Hazard. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 cho nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea. C\u00f3 Hazard tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00fat g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Chelsea ra sao ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;mute=false&amp;vtype=1&amp;playType=0&amp;_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&amp;_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&amp;postroll=true&amp;replay=true&amp;nonVol=true&amp;volume=0.6&amp;boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&amp;nopre=true&amp;midroll=0.8;20s&amp;urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2509","checkdouble":"194778"},{"date":"05:44 19/08","title":"Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</h2><h2>Khi Unai Emery l\u1ea1i xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean th\u1ea5y quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb Unai Emery sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Premier League l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i &quot;ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n&quot;. Unai Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Steve Burtenshaw (1986 - thua ba tr\u1eadn) \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery da thua trong man dau tri voi Maurizio Sarri.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 thua trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 thua trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n. C\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e1ch \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh do Hector Bellerin \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 n\u01a1i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua cho Arsenal. Unai Emery y\u00eau c\u1ea7u hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Pedro th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi Bellerin \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 Marcos Alonso b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng c\u0103ng ngang cho Pedro l\u00e0m b\u00e0n. B\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 ba c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Bellerin khi Hazard c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cho Marcos Alonso l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn thua Man City, c\u1ea3 hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Bellerin tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef. Pep Guardiola s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ed3ng c\u00e1nh Sterling - Mendy \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Bellerin, Maurizio Sarri tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p Willian - Marcos Alonso.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vi tri cua Hector Bellerin lien tuc bi khai thac trong hai tran vua qua.\" title=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c trong hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/bellerin-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c trong hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery v\u1ec1 l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal: Bellerin c\u1ea7n th\u00eam s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Granit Xhaka tr\u00ean s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u01a1i g\u1ea7n Bellerin h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u00edt c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng xu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng. Vi\u1ec7c HLV Unai Emery ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm thay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng Lucas Torreira ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o gi\u00fap Bellerin c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Arsenal tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. Aubameyang v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng... l\u00ean tr\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 bi quan?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 22 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb \u1edf Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Unai Emery b\u1ea5t t\u00e0i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1ch quan chi ph\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal\" title=\"Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018-19.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Arsenal g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd s\u1eb5n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a Emery khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p. Sokratis m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, trong khi Granit Xhaka v\u00e0 Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn HLV Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, b\u1edfi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u00f4ng \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Arsenal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea, HLV Emery t\u1eebng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng r\u00fat c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf ph\u00fat 68 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery co ly do de khong hai long voi mot so cau thu sau khi Arsenal thua tran thu hai lien tiep.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau khi Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau khi Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, hai tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 gh\u00ea g\u1edbm b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Wenger. Thua hai b\u00e0n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh, Arsenal t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn r\u1ed3i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh Rome kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man City \u0111\u0103ng quang hay sao?<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thang-tung-bung-cua-chelsea-truoc-arsenal-172-194778.html\">3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-194777.html\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam-172-194776.html\">Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194775.html\">Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-noi-khung-sau-khi-bi-hoi-ve-tuong-lai-alderweireld-172-194774.html\">Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2508","checkdouble":"194779"},{"date":"15:30 18/08","title":"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd SiamSport \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ec3 t\u00ean 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 \u1edf\u00a0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/cong-phuong_vwzy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ecdt\u00a0danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, t\u1edd SiamSport b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u1eeba qua, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ebfn 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n cho Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Sau hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb pha che ch\u1eafn th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1eddi Olympic Pakistan. V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, SiamSport c\u00f2n nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Son Heung-min, Lee Seung-woo (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c), Beto Goncalves (Indonesia), Mohammed Darwish (Palestine), Adel Bader (Qatar), Zhang Yuning (Trung Qu\u1ed1c), Aung Thu (Myanmar) v\u00e0 Supachai (Th\u00e1i Lan). \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2507","checkdouble":"194745"},{"date":"15:42 18/08","title":"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs Fulham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Fulham v\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Premier League NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18/8.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Tottenham vs Fulham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Fulham v\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Premier League NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18/8.</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2506","checkdouble":"194746"},{"date":"16:21 18/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nguoi-nhat-se-dung-thu-mon-du-bi-de-dau-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh Kojima Ryosuke d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan n\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 Kojima Ryosuke \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat sau va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/a6-3120-1534566074.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Obi Obinna l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, ch\u00ednh HLV Moriyasu Hajime c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i VCK U20 World Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cKojima Ryosuke d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, HLV Moriyasu Hajime cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Obi Obinna cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Obi Obinna l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 77 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft thay cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ryosuke. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1eaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d, Obi n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out.\u00a0<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018-472-194738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018-472-194738.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n sau gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018</span><br />\r\n\u00d4ng Hajime Moriyasu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u1edf ASIAD 18 v\u00ec l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2505","checkdouble":"194747"},{"date":"16:23 18/08","title":"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-london.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea vs Arsenal trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi, c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 Unai Emery. Ai s\u1ebd m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi sau cu\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn derby London \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>1. Arsenal ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf Chelsea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng?</b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Arsenal ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Chelsea ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u2013 nghe m\u1edbi th\u1eadt l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm l\u00e0m sao nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi hai tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch pressing quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc, b\u00f3p ngh\u1eb9t kh\u00f4ng gian gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c. Duy tr\u00ec c\u1ef1 ly nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t quan tr\u1ecdng cho c\u1ea3 khi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1eabn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-nhan-dinh-Chelsea-vs-Arsenal-derby-London-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, Chelsea c\u1ee7a Sarri s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3 r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp v\u00e0 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn derby London kh\u00f4ng Arsene Wenger \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 22 n\u0103m tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Arsenal tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n. K\u1ebf s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Manchester City nh\u01b0ng suy cho c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Emery mu\u1ed1n d\u1eabn d\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2ng cao, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong t\u1ea7m ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 l\u00ean tr\u00ean v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n giao gi\u1eefa hai tri\u1ebft l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp gi\u1eefa Antonio Conte v\u00e0 Sarri r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1eadp b\u1eaby.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">2. Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u00fap Jorginho?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City, Arsenal ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 b\u00f3 h\u1eb9p, v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 trung phong </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:black\">Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang, trong khi Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 Henrikh Mkhitaryan l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng hai c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-London-ky-nguyen-moi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh 4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ozil \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Arsenal. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ngay ngo\u00e0i r\u00eca v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u00edt ch\u1ea1m trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean tr\u00ean cho Aubameyang v\u00e0 Ramsey.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd Jorginho v\u1eabn \u0111ang v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10 thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh Emery \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u00fd th\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Ozil v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c x\u1edbi tung tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1ed1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m.<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">3. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Guendouzi?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">T\u1eeb Napoli \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea, b\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sarri s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n bao g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, m\u1ed9t box-to-box v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi m\u1eaft x\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng kia th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00f3 (Lorenzo Insigne \u1edf Napoli v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u1edf Chelsea).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i cho Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby London b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Matteo Guendouzi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb non n\u1edbt, thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n m\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Premier League.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-London-ky-nguyen-moi-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Guendouzi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh anh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn trong b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1eaft b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1edbi Petr Cech.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 ba tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Sarri, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Jorginho v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi N\u2019Golo Kante? T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea r\u1ea5t th\u00edch Ross Barkley nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Mateo Kovacic, t\u00e2n binh Croatia m\u1edbi m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Real Madrid, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">4. Hazard v\u00e0 Pedro c\u00e0y n\u00e1t hai c\u00e1nh Arsenal?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi \u1edf Emirates khi c\u1ea3 ba s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng (Sead Kolasinac, Nacho Monreal, </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Ainsley Maitland-Niles)<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nbold\">, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed g\u00e2y \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea5t cho t\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u1edfi \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean m\u00e0 v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u00f3 h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn? Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4 l\u1eadp </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\ncolor:black\">Maitland-Niles v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Stephan Lichtsteiner tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o sau \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng cho Riyad Mahrez, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 Sarri l\u01b0u t\u00e2m cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Pedro Rodriguez.<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"5 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/5-cau-hoi-cho-duoc-tra-loi-trong-tran-derby-London-ky-nguyen-moi-hinh-anh-4.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">H\u00e0nh lang \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00ean kia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n cho Arsenal, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1edd n\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Hector Bellerin v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch d\u00e2ng cao, trong khi Lacazette d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn thuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean. Ozil c\u00f3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao \u1edf kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y, v\u1eady n\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Lucas Torreira, t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay t\u1eebng b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea3 Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i World Cup 2018 h\u01a1n th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">5. Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Chelsea?<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng David Luiz ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng minh ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi b\u1ecf r\u01a1i anh tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1ea5t lu\u1eadn ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh hay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Huddersfield Town, n\u01a1i anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Steve Mounie v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang Lacazette\" title=\"Aubameyang Lacazette\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/hoc-tro-mach-emery-cach-dua-arsenal-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Antonio Rudiger c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t y\u1ebfu trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadp trung. N\u00f3i c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng oan, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1edfi Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri cho l\u00e0m quen vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ed1ng hai trong b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda ti\u1ebfng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c d\u00f9 thua Man City, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t gi\u00fap Arsenal d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 co c\u1ee5m h\u01a1n, Lacazette ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi Aubameyang t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1eb7p song s\u00e1t xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf Stamford Bridge.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m ra sao c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Gabon n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 reo r\u1eafc kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 cho m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed3 chi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p nh\u01b0 Luiz v\u00e0 Rudiger. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;color:black\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London:<br>\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do-172-194717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do-172-194717.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal (23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8): \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y Man City l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o</span><br>\r\nUnai Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Brigde v\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt ni\u1ec1m tin cho Arsenal, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n trong khi Maurizio Sarri...